sentences: Mireille Bauer (born 24 August 1951, Barr, Alsace, northeastern France) is a French percussionist and former member of Gong.
She subsequently left the band and joined progressive rock/fusion band Edition Speciale (1978-9).
In the 1980s, she played in John Greaves' backing band, working alongside Fran√ßois Ovide.
She subsequently worked with Art Zoyd in the 1990s.
